        <title>Comprehensive Holocaust Accountability in Insurance Measure</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To clarify the authority of States to establish conditions for insurers to conduct the business of insurance within a State based on provision of information regarding Holocaust era insurance policies of the insurer and to establish a Federal cause of action for claims for payment of such insurance policies, and for other purposes.</title>
      </item>
